            <div class="d-none m-btm-half" id="PlaceholderAd-1">
            </div>
            <h2>
             How-to Gain More VIP Points
            </h2>
            <p>
             Once you've got your Shift Account linked to your Vault Insider account, you can start doing things that will gain you points right away! You can check out all of the ways to gain points right
             <a href="https://borderlands.com/en-US/vip-activities/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
              here
             </a>
             ! For the curious, here's some of the ways they can be gained:
            </p>
            <ul>
             <li>
              Take a Borderlands 3 Pre-Order Survey (If you've pre-ordered): 250 Points
             </li>
             <li>
              Link a 2k Account or Twitch Account: 750 Points
             </li>
             <li>
              Take a VIP Season 1 Survey: 250 Points
             </li>
             <li>
              Watch Borderlands 3 Trailers/Videos: 250 Points
             </li>
             <li>
              Check out Borderlands on social media platforms: 100 Points per Week
             </li>
             <li>
              Many more...
             </li>
            </ul>
            <h2>
             VIP Rewards
            </h2>
            <p>
             VIP Rewards include various cosmetics, golden keys, wallpapers, and even weapons for the game! Take a look at all of the rewards right
             <a href="https://borderlands.com/en-US/vip-rewards/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
              here
             </a>
             . While you are there, you might as well spin the Weaponizer and receive a free weapon for Borderlands 2 &amp; 3!
            </p>
            <h3>
             Heads &amp; Skins
            </h3>
            <p>
             <img alt="" class="aligncenter size-site-large wp-image-25557 lazyload" data-src="https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-vip-rewards-cosmetics-816x397.jpg" data-srcset="https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-vip-rewards-cosmetics-816x397.jpg 816w, https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-vip-rewards-cosmetics-300x146.jpg 300w, https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-vip-rewards-cosmetics-768x374.jpg 768w, https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-vip-rewards-cosmetics-398x194.jpg 398w, https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-vip-rewards-cosmetics.jpg 1000w" height="397" sizes="(max-width: 816px) 100vw, 816px" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" width="816"/>
             <noscript>
              <img alt="" class="aligncenter size-site-large wp-image-25557" height="397" sizes="(max-width: 816px) 100vw, 816px" src="https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-vip-rewards-cosmetics-816x397.jpg" srcset="https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-vip-rewards-cosmetics-816x397.jpg 816w, https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-vip-rewards-cosmetics-300x146.jpg 300w, https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-vip-rewards-cosmetics-768x374.jpg 768w, https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-vip-rewards-cosmetics-398x194.jpg 398w, https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-vip-rewards-cosmetics.jpg 1000w" width="816"/>
             </noscript>
            </p>
            <p>
             There are currently eight different cosmetics you can purchase with VIP points, two for each character. The heads cost 4,000 and the skins cost 3,000 points.
            </p>
            <h3>
             Golden Keys
            </h3>
            <p>
             Keys are available for 1,500 points, but you can't currently purchase them for Borderlands 3. They are only available for the previous games. I wouldn't waste your points on these, there's still a lot of Shift Keys floating around for those games at the moment.
            </p>
            <h3>
             Wallpapers
            </h3>
            <p>
             If you want to dress up your desktop or mobile device, you can purchase wallpapers for 500 points each.
            </p>
            <h3>
             Guns
            </h3>
            <p>
             <img alt="" class="aligncenter size-site-large wp-image-25561 lazyload" data-src="https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-legendary-maliwan-gun-816x397.jpg" data-srcset="https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-legendary-maliwan-gun-816x397.jpg 816w, https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-legendary-maliwan-gun-300x146.jpg 300w, https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-legendary-maliwan-gun-768x374.jpg 768w, https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-legendary-maliwan-gun-398x194.jpg 398w, https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-legendary-maliwan-gun.jpg 1000w" height="397" sizes="(max-width: 816px) 100vw, 816px" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" width="816"/>
             <noscript>
              <img alt="" class="aligncenter size-site-large wp-image-25561" height="397" sizes="(max-width: 816px) 100vw, 816px" src="https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-legendary-maliwan-gun-816x397.jpg" srcset="https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-legendary-maliwan-gun-816x397.jpg 816w, https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-legendary-maliwan-gun-300x146.jpg 300w, https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-legendary-maliwan-gun-768x374.jpg 768w, https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-legendary-maliwan-gun-398x194.jpg 398w, https://progameguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/borderlands3-legendary-maliwan-gun.jpg 1000w" width="816"/>
             </noscript>
            </p>
            <p>
             Believe it or not, you can purchase guns with your points as well. For 4,000 points you can purchase a variety of different guns, some for each game in the franchise. The Borderlands 3 options are level 10, so they could be useful to you while you are leveling up. These weapons count towards the eight reward weapons you need to obtain to unlock the special legendary Maliwan weapon for Borderlands 3!
            </p>
           </body>
          </html>
         </div>
